			<p class="center center reveal fromBottom">
				While working on <abbr title="LEGO® Star Wars™ Battles">LSWB</abbr> I contributed to multiple areas of the game's development.
			</p>

			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Feature Lead For <abbr title="Artificial Intelligence">AI</abbr></h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				I designed, implemented and supported our <abbr title="Artificial Intelligence">AI</abbr> systems that caters for a number of different requirements.
				<ul>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Teach players how to play the game</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Human skill level opponent at each skill level for times of low liquidity</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Give the player an opponent to play when offline</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Automated testing of the game</li>
				</ul>
			</p>


			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Feature Lead For Audio</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				This role involved:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Capturing new audio assets and systems required for each feature</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Reviewing created audio</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Creating or overseeing creation of audio event triggers </li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Coding audio systems</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Designing our audio creation workflows</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Maintaining and updating our <a href="https://www.fmod.com/" target="_blank">FMOD</a> integration</li>
			</ul>


			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">improving Studio work flows</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				During my time at TT Odyssey, I have been recognised for improving multiple workflows across the studio.
				<ul>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Unit testing</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Code reviews using github's pull request workflow</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Automated integration testing using my <abbr title="Artificial Intelligence">AI</abbr></li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Improving pre-production documents</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">How we onboard new starters</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">How we hand over from leaving employees</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Made our stand-up meetings more streamlined</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Contributed heavily to retrospectives</li>
					<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Client side unit testing</li>
				</ul>
			</p>

			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Server Tools</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">We created multiple web tools to help support our develop of the game.</p>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">I create a tool to capture snapshots of players profiles in both dev and live environments from any version, this tool dramatical reduced time needed to fix bugs.</p>

