			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Localisation</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				I created our localisation system that supports 17 languages:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">English</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Arabic</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Danish</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Dutch</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">French</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">German</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Italian</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Japanese</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Korean</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Malay</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Portuguese</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Russian</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Simplified Chinese</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Traditional Chinese</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Turkish</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				This system also caterers for each language's cultures differences such as:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">pluralisations</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Genders</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Punctuation</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft"><abbr title="Right To Left">RTL</abbr> / <abbr title="Left To Right">LTR</abbr></li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Making the UI responsive to extreme string lengths</li>
			</ul>

			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Optimisation</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				As our game has to run on low spec mobile devices it is critical that we test and optimize the performance of are app on devices regularly to maintain a shippable build.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Profiling</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Cleaning up garbage allocations</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Caching</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">Pooling</li>
				<li class="center reveal fromLeft">reducing Code run time</li>
			</ul>


